  <title>Past Flyers</title>

  <para>
    Here are a collection of sample flyers which we have used to
    advertise speakers for a variety of events. Each flyer contains a
    short bit of text describing the event and all of the relevant
    information needed to attend. Make sure to include links to
    website post and/or QR codes so that students can just use their
    phone to bookmark the event quickly.
  </para>
  
